Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻過所有的雜誌也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這搖頭嘆息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 與我相稱的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.69,0:00:30.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都無法 討得你的歡心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉讓你失望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本不像我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你  別用那種冷冷的眼神望著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我照著自己的步調去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話我很快就會崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.34,0:22:00.35,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.84,0:22:06.02,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  這就是愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.26,0:22:11.44,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手尋找溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.53,0:22:17.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  奇蹟也一定會發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.87,0:22:30.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有愛 就絕對有具體的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.71,0:22:41.26,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 現在 在我手中 有誕生的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.47,0:22:49.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神飽滿  也不能  太過勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.86,0:22:54.78,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.28,0:23:05.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起來  培育茁壯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.56,0:00:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬間明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.61,0:00:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開始就不會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.44,0:00:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱熱鬧鬧的暑假才剛剛開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.73,0:00:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子的對像是什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.92,0:00:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.58,0:00:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.60,0:00:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.38,0:01:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在盛夏到伊豆去做海水浴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.30,0:01:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟小蘭卻遇到了一件奇怪的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.56,0:01:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為園子竟然交了一個姓道脇的男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.94,0:01:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就在她開開心心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.23,0:01:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著請吃晚餐的道脇先生去接她的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.68,0:01:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子卻遭到了不明人士的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.80,0:02:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是我多心才覺得總有人在監視我們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.93,0:02:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭說的那個在哪見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.07,0:02:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴眼鏡的人也很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.55,0:02:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有攻擊園子的歹徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.20,0:02:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人真的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個單純的小偷嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.60,0:02:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子危險的夏日物語(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.29,0:02:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.53,0:02:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的餐廳哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.34,0:02:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這裡好像沒有什麼客人來嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.65,0:02:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們好像來得太早了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.39,0:02:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的不跟我們過去啊？ 園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.53,0:03:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天晚上在被窩裡面一直想起那個男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒辦法好好睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.71,0:03:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在這裡睡一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.19,0:03:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那好可惜哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.94,0:03:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在小冰箱裡面放了很多的飲料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.19,0:03:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳渴的話自己拿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.69,0:03:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.95,0:03:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走囉 園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們儘管慢慢吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.36,0:03:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你覺得睡夠了的話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.16,0:03:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你待會就自己來餐廳哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.38,0:03:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.09,0:03:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的海鮮禦膳真的非常好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來是想讓園子也嘗一嘗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.61,0:03:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.29,0:03:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子她沒有問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛車子還在發動中耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.58,0:03:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把冷氣打開了 放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好豐盛哦 這是一人份嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 既豐盛又便宜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.60,0:04:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是這家餐廳受歡迎的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早的就吃全餐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 這裡的料理沒話說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 好好吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃得快要撐死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.74,0:04:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要謝謝你請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.49,0:04:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都覺得有點對不起園子了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是旅館的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.85,0:04:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也常常到這家餐廳來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 今天是我第一次來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.72,0:04:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個咖啡色頭髮的女孩上哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.89,0:04:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼一直沒有見到她人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說園子啊 她昨天晚上沒有睡好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在外面的車子裡補眠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.20,0:04:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.10,0:05:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道脇哥哥的車子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子怎麼會動呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 前面就是懸崖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.32,0:05:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧 歡迎下次再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.68,0:05:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有付錢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.88,0:05:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.86,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開車鎖的工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手煞車被人放下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.11,0:05:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子 快醒醒啊 園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣跑根本沒有辦法使力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 沒剩多少距離了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.69,0:05:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 離開這輛車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.21,0:06:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子 快抓住我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.92,0:06:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好 大家都沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.68,0:06:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當時為什麼不把手煞車拉上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少胡說 我當然有拉上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我沒有拉手煞車的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子早就已經掉到懸崖下麵去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有人把手煞車放下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他利用開車鎖的工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把車鎖給撬開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.31,0:06:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是企圖謀害園子姐姐的不明人士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.07,0:07:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子在車上睡覺的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.08,0:07:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個人把車鎖給撬開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再把手煞車給放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來就可以慢慢地讓車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.56,0:07:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順著坡道滑到懸崖下麵去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.95,0:07:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據潛水人員的報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛掉到海裡面的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手煞車的確沒有拉起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.38,0:07:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外我們還在路上發現了這個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是開車鎖的工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹徒是一個行家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的指紋都已經被擦乾淨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.98,0:07:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外 還有沒有什麼線索？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.35,0:07:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前唯一發現的是就在停車的那個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.83,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流了一灘從車子空調上流出來的水而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.39,0:07:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時妳有沒有看到可疑的人物在車子的附近徘徊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.79,0:07:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 因為昨天沒怎麼睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.21,0:07:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以剛才在車子裡面睡得很熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.65,0:08:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要說起來 從我們到伊豆以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.37,0:08:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會莫名其妙出現在我們附近的可疑人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊倒是有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.02,0:08:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 請問你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.72,0:08:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在他們下榻旅館服務的職員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.81,0:08:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天會到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.33,0:08:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為旅館白天的工作沒有那麼繁重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.34,0:08:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才抽了點空到這裡來喝杯茶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢夥絕對不是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子向下滑的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.88,0:08:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就已經走到我們當時吃飯的餐廳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.88,0:08:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說他是先將車門撬開之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.72,0:08:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將手煞車放下再趕到餐廳的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.79,0:08:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從餐廳入口進去的時候 我們應該會注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.16,0:08:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據餐廳的人表示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.61,0:08:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餐廳的後門當時是上著鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們注意到他的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.40,0:08:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正好從洗手間出來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餐廳的洗手間裡沒有可以爬到外面的窗戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也不可能是道脇先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.11,0:09:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他一直跟我們在同一張桌子上進餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中間也沒有離席過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.24,0:09:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.82,0:09:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最可疑的就是那個一直跟蹤監視我們的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在場的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.59,0:09:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細經過等到了局裡再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 大家請上車吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要坐車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.12,0:09:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我現在真的很不想坐車耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有點害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.06,0:09:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣園子你就跟我一塊走到警局好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.62,0:09:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡走過去不是很遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.53,0:09:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊看看風景還可以緩解情緒怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.05,0:09:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就這麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是妳又遭到攻擊那可怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子妳的頭髮又是咖啡色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.50,0:10:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個歹徒跟那個命案的兇手很有可能是同一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.13,0:10:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官你不用太擔心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他再怎麼大膽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能光天化日下手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.13,0:10:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 要是有個萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.82,0:10:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心吧 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.82,0:10:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道脇先生陪著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要有什麼萬一的話還有小蘭保護啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.31,0:10:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 這樣你們可別繞到其他地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要直接到警局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.05,0:10:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.37,0:10:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是昨天在旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.94,0:10:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是今天在車上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.51,0:10:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真是多災多難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.97,0:10:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子 妳真的沒有什麼印象嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.69,0:10:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此可見 妳有獨特的魅力哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.26,0:10:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹徒為什麼要攻擊園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.33,0:10:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要她的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.92,0:11:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不在他撬開車門的時候一刀刺死她呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.25,0:11:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必要故意讓車子滑動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.26,0:11:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順勢掉下懸崖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.17,0:11:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種方式花的功夫反而更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.01,0:11:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我們本來打算吃完飯後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.45,0:11:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就順便回家而把行李都放車上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在全都一起燒光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.53,0:11:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎麼偏偏是我碰上這種倒楣的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.42,0:11:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還不算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我損失的可是車子耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.24,0:11:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從認識了我以後 實在給你添太多麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也沒那麼嚴重啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.61,0:11:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟妳拍的照片比起來這不算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片可是金錢買不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.23,0:11:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果到最後留下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.78,0:11:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有那一張照片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一張？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.65,0:11:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳忘啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要給新一看的那張照片啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.79,0:11:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直帶在身上 你可以放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.21,0:11:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還帶著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.15,0:11:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳再鬧的話我可要生氣囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.16,0:12:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹徒真正的目的的果然是要銷毀那些照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.43,0:12:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才有必要將車子跟園子的行李一起摔下懸崖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.65,0:12:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.49,0:12:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹徒怎麼會認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.77,0:12:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子拍到了他不能為人所知的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.71,0:12:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看過園子拍的那些照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.87,0:12:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面根本沒有類似的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.16,0:12:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說有我疏忽掉的地方嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.16,0:12:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那個傢夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們好像被人家跟蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.33,0:12:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.10,0:12:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用跑的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.31,0:12:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.67,0:12:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們趕快追上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.13,0:13:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到這種樹林裡來反而會更危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.97,0:13:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會 這樣才安全啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.27,0:13:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.20,0:13:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我們兵分兩路把他包圍起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.39,0:13:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.63,0:13:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他就是兇手的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.42,0:13:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還想對園子不利呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.66,0:13:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片早就燒掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.84,0:13:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是昨天發現屍體的樹林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.03,0:13:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們前天晚上經過這的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電車也剛好經過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.00,0:13:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼 有什麼不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 把他們給跟丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下事情可就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.76,0:14:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底鬧夠了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.86,0:14:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是以為我們會一直逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.73,0:14:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就大錯特錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.51,0:14:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你要穿著一雙拖鞋就跑到樹林裡面來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.47,0:14:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在旅館裡面攻擊園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.92,0:14:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才又讓車子墜落懸崖對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.52,0:14:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再怎麼解釋都沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手上的毛就是證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要好好的看清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.44,0:14:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子昨天晚上在你的手臂上留下的齒痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.95,0:14:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.04,0:14:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會沒有齒痕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.43,0:14:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在另外一隻手對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.79,0:14:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻手上也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢 你到底是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.28,0:15:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是千葉縣警局的刑警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要以為亮出了這種證件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.52,0:15:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人就會輕而易舉的相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.44,0:15:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可告訴你 我父親以前也做過員警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.04,0:15:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我清楚得很
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.57,0:15:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有必要要出示員警身份的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.71,0:15:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定要翻出永久用紙的第一頁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.75,0:15:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是正確的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.40,0:15:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫寺林省二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.54,0:15:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.47,0:15:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我正在追蹤一個案件的嫌疑犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.78,0:15:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌疑犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.10,0:15:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.29,0:15:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般穿拖鞋的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是不穿襪子的對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.79,0:15:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.84,0:15:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子有危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.85,0:15:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.06,0:15:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我踩到樹枝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.93,0:15:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子我們跑進樹林裡來真的是錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.44,0:15:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.01,0:15:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齒痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼會嚇成這個樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.28,0:16:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒什麼好怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.58,0:16:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是昨晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.13,0:16:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在我腿上留下的齒痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.13,0:16:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實園子昨晚咬到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.11,0:16:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.27,0:16:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是小腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.42,0:16:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光線太暗她才誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手會認為園子拍到照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.01,0:16:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.74,0:16:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電車行駛時電架摩擦所發出的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.31,0:16:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在犯案的時候光線來自身後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.91,0:16:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行兇之後又看到園子拿著照相機從樹林的旁邊經過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.66,0:16:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才會誤會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以為園子看到他跟被害者在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也說過那句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.73,0:16:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放在心上 妳不管怎麼穿都很迷人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 浴衣和泳裝也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.85,0:17:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子到這之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.59,0:17:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在前天看煙火的時候才穿過浴衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們昨天才跟這個傢夥認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.13,0:17:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能看過園子穿浴衣的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.93,0:17:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我沒有早注意到這一點呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.33,0:17:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.87,0:17:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把照片拿出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.84,0:17:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妳拍了那張要給那個偵探看的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在妳看來也許以為那是情侶親熱的畫面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.92,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳拍到我行兇的過程了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和這一幕一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.63,0:17:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四…四個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說道脇先生殺了四個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.02,0:17:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果昨天的被害人也是他殺的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.39,0:17:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就是四個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.77,0:17:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道他為何只找咖啡色頭髮的女子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.72,0:17:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從很久以前我就已經盯上他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.95,0:17:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候只是為了一件偷車案逮捕他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於殺人案件證據還不足夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.20,0:17:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是聽說伊豆這裡也發生了類似的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.37,0:17:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才過來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然又讓我看到那個傢夥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.76,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我趕到的時候他已經犯案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.15,0:18:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時他明明一直呆在餐廳裏頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.97,0:18:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能讓車子自己滑動呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.55,0:18:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用冰塊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.66,0:18:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.59,0:18:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他車上有小冰箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.16,0:18:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他先拿出一個楔子形狀的冰塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.14,0:18:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在左輪的輪胎下麵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.14,0:18:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止車子向前滑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.19,0:18:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後假裝對著留在車內的園子說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順勢把手煞車放了下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.61,0:18:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著再把開車鎖的工具丟在路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.68,0:18:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是要混淆警方的搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.14,0:18:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.88,0:18:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他之所以會預留兩個停車格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.55,0:18:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了避免其他車子會停在他車子的前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.18,0:18:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都會以為那只是車上空調流出的水而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.05,0:18:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他只攻擊咖啡色頭髮的女子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.74,0:18:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被女朋友狠心的甩掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.79,0:19:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要一看到妳這種聒噪的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心裡就會自然而然的開始冒火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.82,0:19:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳和那個陷我於萬丈深淵的女人一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.55,0:19:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有一頭咖啡色的頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快看那裡 那不是園子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.37,0:19:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.85,0:19:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.97,0:19:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 這是為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.49,0:19:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼對我有意的男人都是這種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天爺我恨你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你的手...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.82,0:19:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.97,0:19:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直覺得在哪里見過那個戴眼鏡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.55,0:19:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是在比賽的會場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.48,0:19:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是杯戶高中空手道的主將
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.06,0:20:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人稱「踢擊美男子」的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京極真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.96,0:20:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢夥還真是危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.70,0:20:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是有我這種悠閒人常在旁邊出現那就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠閒人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.41,0:20:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你一直都在我的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.18,0:20:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直跟在你們的後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你們進樹林之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.68,0:20:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有被當成跟蹤狂的心理準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢夥在遇到你們之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.73,0:20:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾經跟兩三個女孩子搭訕過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.49,0:20:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一直有點擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.59,0:20:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要保護我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.40,0:20:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個又不認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.45,0:20:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也許不知道我是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.43,0:20:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我曾經在空手道的比賽會場看過妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.78,0:20:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時拼了命地在為朋友加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的倩影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.58,0:20:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是沒有想到妳會這麼巧投宿到我家的旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.62,0:21:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.31,0:21:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種故意要挑起男人注意那種類似內衣的穿著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.02,0:21:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勸妳以後能不穿還是不要再穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.41,0:21:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.64,0:21:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是對妳有好感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.46,0:21:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一之中的一個男孩的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.92,0:21:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳不領情也無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.36,0:23:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京極要到外國留學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.47,0:23:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.91,0:23:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個在那之後不是處得很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.91,0:23:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他說日本已經沒有強勁的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.92,0:23:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要到那裡去深造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.01,0:23:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.17,0:23:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起去看棒球社的友誼賽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.04,0:23:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是高一的棒球主力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.39,0:23:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說不但人長得帥 也很受歡迎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.15,0:23:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是還說要等京極回來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.67,0:23:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.99,0:23:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.49,0:23:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.72,0:23:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙在水裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.46,0:23:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.13,0:23:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.32,0:24:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人是不可能從那個地方進出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.84,0:24:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是用了什麼手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.09,0:24:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這個浴室變成密室的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.89,0:24:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.41,0:24:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水中的鑰匙密室事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.05,0:24:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.48,0:24:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠟筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.26,0:24:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的事件是鑰匙上的鐵圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.74,0:24:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說啥 我聽不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.10,0:24:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻 不告訴妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.20,0:24:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這梗還真老
